Description: AllStar Link node monitoring dashboard (Supermon-ng)
 Supermon-ng provides a web UI for monitoring and controlling AllStar Link
 nodes: AMI integration, WebSocket live status, favorites, DVSwitch,
 announcements (upload, TTS, playback, cron scheduling), and node status/weather
 updates via systemd timers.
 .
 This package installs the application under /var/www/html/supermon-ng,
 configures Apache (modules, site, SSL), systemd units, and sudoers rules.
 See /var/www/html/supermon-ng/docs/DEBIAN.md for debconf and upgrade options.
